metadata.name: Mountain Waves
metadata.description:
"Her march is o'er the mountain waves,  
Her home is on the deep."

This artwork was originally released as a limited set of 5 physical pen plots. Now, it is the ground zero for my very first foray into minting NFTs. Please join me here, on the ground floor.

Plottable SVG generated and designed by @WythDryden.
